text: Novosvobodnaya () is a rural locality (a stanitsa) in Abadzekhskoye Rural Settlement of Maykopsky District, Russia. The population was 591 as of 2018. There are 25 streets. == Geography == The stanitsa is located in 19 km to the east from Abadzekhskaya. == References == Category:Rural localities in Maykopsky District
title: Novosvobodnaya
